1b69fa0a-d375-4497-bd2f-a12631f60689.title: Gypsy Aris
1b69fa0a-d375-4497-bd2f-a12631f60689.text:
Cross my palm with silver and the future will be
revealed to you.

options.text: Ok, here you go.
Who are you calling young one?!
No, I don't believe in that stuff.
With silver?

47d862a4-e7bb-4939-a658-d78cd8caf04b.title: <player>
47d862a4-e7bb-4939-a658-d78cd8caf04b.text: Oh dear. I don't seem to have enough money.

184ec9b2-76ba-4619-96db-8b28d0505251.title: Gypsy Aris
184ec9b2-76ba-4619-96db-8b28d0505251.text:
Come closer, and listen carefully to what the future
holds for you, as I peer into the swirling mists of the
crystal ball.

45d69562-4ea6-4260-9e39-a7fb5c56f5b6.title: Gypsy Aris
45d69562-4ea6-4260-9e39-a7fb5c56f5b6.text: I can see images forming. I can see you.

e07b2ed5-c79c-4223-a4c8-40f4c2f2be3a.title: Gypsy Aris
e07b2ed5-c79c-4223-a4c8-40f4c2f2be3a.text:
You are holding a very impressive looking sword. I'm
sure I recognise that sword...

594aeb07-5460-4505-b48c-453de7116844.title: Gypsy Aris
594aeb07-5460-4505-b48c-453de7116844.text: There is a big dark shadow appearing now.

2227b184-93d5-454f-870d-5248f28a053d.title: <player>
2227b184-93d5-454f-870d-5248f28a053d.text:
Oh! I really hope he didn't see me looking at him
through my crystal ball!

b312802b-547b-4e4e-a2be-0a953d10b706.title: Gypsy Aris
b312802b-547b-4e4e-a2be-0a953d10b706.text:
He tried to destroy this city 150 years ago. He was
stopped just in time by the great hero Wally.

602b9034-9663-4c2f-a9d4-b748083791e7.title: Gypsy Aris
602b9034-9663-4c2f-a9d4-b748083791e7.text:
Using his magic sword Silverlight, Wally managed to
trap the demon in the stone circle just south
of this city.

cb2b404b-d036-4a39-90cf-d559e3ba626b.title: Gypsy Aris
cb2b404b-d036-4a39-90cf-d559e3ba626b.text:
Ye gods! Silverlight was the sword you were holding in
my vision! You are the one destined to stop the demon
this time.

options.text: How am I meant to fight a demon who can destroy cities?
Okay, where is he? I'll kill him for you!
Wally doesn't sound like a very heroic name.

ece766f0-d509-447b-88e2-ec2ea46be51c.title: <player>
ece766f0-d509-447b-88e2-ec2ea46be51c.text:
How am I meant to fight a demon who can destroy
cities?!

88f5149f-9096-48d6-b000-2e722a931f48.title: Gypsy Aris
88f5149f-9096-48d6-b000-2e722a931f48.text:
If you face Delrith while he is still weak from being
summoned, and use the correct weapon, you will not
find the task too arduous.

35f1c8d9-740b-4988-8c5c-8ba7b56383e4.title: Gypsy Aris
35f1c8d9-740b-4988-8c5c-8ba7b56383e4.text:
Do not fear. If you follow the path of the great hero
Wally, then you are sure to defeat the demon.

a2261c8f-9330-4630-bc65-68f52d07f901.title: <player>
a2261c8f-9330-4630-bc65-68f52d07f901.text: Okay, where is he? I'll kill him for you

0d70cf01-08c7-42d0-8675-a4f54de06ee3.title: Gypsy Aris
0d70cf01-08c7-42d0-8675-a4f54de06ee3.text: Ah, the overconfidence of the young!

cfeed69a-7c31-477e-89dd-8d64689ce700.title: Gypsy Aris
cfeed69a-7c31-477e-89dd-8d64689ce700.text:
Delrith can't be harmed by ordinary weapons. You
must face him using the same weapon that Wally used.

1a799c48-820d-4a47-89eb-908631eb4cbe.title: <player>
1a799c48-820d-4a47-89eb-908631eb4cbe.text: Wally doesn't sound a very heroic name.

1eb034e4-676c-44d3-9117-5280025e30b9.title: Gypsy Aris
1eb034e4-676c-44d3-9117-5280025e30b9.text:
Yes I know. Maybe that is why history doesn't
remember him. However he was a very great hero.

02d871ff-8296-432d-892b-ac37d54199fd.title: Gypsy Aris
02d871ff-8296-432d-892b-ac37d54199fd.text:
Who knows how much pain and suffering Delrith would
have brought forth without Wally to stop him!

b1163c09-878d-4d05-a680-c772d88217cc.title: Gypsy Aris
b1163c09-878d-4d05-a680-c772d88217cc.text:
It looks like you are going to need to perform similar
heroics.

options.text: How am I meant to fight a demon who can destroy cities?
Okay, where is he? I'll kill him for you!
So how did Wally kill Delrith?

54c7d770-30b0-4100-95c2-c7a0ec37825f.title: <player>
54c7d770-30b0-4100-95c2-c7a0ec37825f.text: So how did Wally kill Delrith?

dae4bbc7-8360-4112-8ba3-07db2471e3ae.title: Gypsy Aris
dae4bbc7-8360-4112-8ba3-07db2471e3ae.text:
Wally managed to arrive at the stone circle just as
Delrith was summoned by a cult of chaos druids...

ec90ecaa-c894-4bf9-ab7b-3a56eb90a38d.title: Gypsy Aris
ec90ecaa-c894-4bf9-ab7b-3a56eb90a38d.text: Now, what was that incantation again?

d4b8041e-5810-4b81-a3d2-ad7aa715c490.title: Gypsy Aris
d4b8041e-5810-4b81-a3d2-ad7aa715c490.text: I am the greatest demon slayer EVER!

946b16c9-db9a-4039-b481-f1031746df5d.title: Gypsy Aris
946b16c9-db9a-4039-b481-f1031746df5d.text:
By reciting the correct magical incantation, and
thrusting Silverlight into Delrith while he was newly
summoned, Wally was able to imprison Delrith in the
stone block in the centre of the circle.

587d93bb-b095-4d32-a4a9-22f500f9aab1.title: Gypsy Aris
587d93bb-b095-4d32-a4a9-22f500f9aab1.text: Delrith will come forth from the stone circle again.

6518b44d-dad5-4e59-8fb7-1a085777eaf9.title: Gypsy Aris
6518b44d-dad5-4e59-8fb7-1a085777eaf9.text:
I would imagine an evil sorcerer is already starting on
the rituals to summon Delrith as we speak.

options.text: How am I meant to fight a demon who can destroy cities?
Okay, where is he? I'll kill him for you!
What is the magical incantation?
Where can I find Silverlight?
Okay, thanks. I'll do my best to stop the demon.

ea03bdec-22c1-492c-97c2-da9a1dbc6302.title: Gypsy Aris
ea03bdec-22c1-492c-97c2-da9a1dbc6302.text: Oh yes, let me think a second...

3c20d560-28f1-4800-920d-68ca803b6065.title: Gypsy Aris
3c20d560-28f1-4800-920d-68ca803b6065.text:
Alright, I think I've got it now, it goes.... Purchai...
Gabindo... Carlem... Aber... Camerinthum. Have you got
that?

8de95a09-ef64-4d1e-aa81-5f0230ac46e0.title: <player>
8de95a09-ef64-4d1e-aa81-5f0230ac46e0.text: Ok thanks. I'll do my best to stop the demon.

005570ae-0d6f-4e83-8d12-a2e967022b4a.title: Gypsy Aris
005570ae-0d6f-4e83-8d12-a2e967022b4a.text: Good luck, and may Guthix be with you!

0b71a7d5-d853-4649-b8d8-a3fde2615c22.title: Gypsy Aris
0b71a7d5-d853-4649-b8d8-a3fde2615c22.text:
Silverlight has been passed down through Wally's
descendants. I believe it is currently in the care of one
of the King's knights called Sir Prysin.

705bd3a8-ea35-4a83-a708-f1a9e57a0229.title: Gypsy Aris
705bd3a8-ea35-4a83-a708-f1a9e57a0229.text:
He shouldn't be too hard to find. He lives in the royal
palace in this city. Tell him Gypsy Aris sent you.

79784d69-c986-407e-aaef-d1807dc01ec2.title: <player>
79784d69-c986-407e-aaef-d1807dc01ec2.text: Who are you calling young one?!

a0376011-c69b-4168-8145-1bb8c1cd6b83.title: Gypsy Aris
a0376011-c69b-4168-8145-1bb8c1cd6b83.text:
You have been on this world a relatively short time. At
least compared to me.

7d5cb809-230f-47d3-bab7-af7116e6f427.title: Gypsy Aris
7d5cb809-230f-47d3-bab7-af7116e6f427.text: So, do you want your fortune told or not?

options.text: Yes please.
No, I don't believe in that stuff.
Ooh how old are you then?

921b5da3-8577-480d-8e59-f2b41aa9ecbc.title: Gypsy Aris
921b5da3-8577-480d-8e59-f2b41aa9ecbc.text: Cross my palm with silver then.

options.text: Ok here you go.
Oh you want me to pay. No thanks.

7518ee3d-9fe8-4df8-ad5f-f612de9f92ab.title: <player>
7518ee3d-9fe8-4df8-ad5f-f612de9f92ab.text: Oh you want me to pay. No thanks.

8fce5789-9354-4448-ae0d-142942d391ee.title: <player>
8fce5789-9354-4448-ae0d-142942d391ee.text: No, I don't believe in that stuff.

4aab8199-b613-4f13-9cdf-d292222353ad.title: Gypsy Aris
4aab8199-b613-4f13-9cdf-d292222353ad.text:
Oh, sorry, I forgot. With gold, I mean. They haven't
used silver coins since before you were born! So, do
you want your fortune told?

options.text: Ok here you go.
No, I don't believe in that stuff.
What is the magical incantation?
Where can I find Silverlight?
Stop calling me that!
Well I'd better press on with it.

34247ce0-f1fe-4430-b6ea-2b10d1c35699.title: Gypsy Aris
34247ce0-f1fe-4430-b6ea-2b10d1c35699.text: Oh yes, let me think a second...

5b54c0e8-1f16-428c-be2c-942d5db97e69.title: Gypsy Aris
5b54c0e8-1f16-428c-be2c-942d5db97e69.text:
Alright, I think I've got it now, it goes.... Purchai...
Gabindo... Carlem... Aber... Camerinthum. Have you got
that?

5d1abad8-99b0-44f0-8a55-197d93145875.title: Gypsy Aris
5d1abad8-99b0-44f0-8a55-197d93145875.text:
Silverlight has been passed down through Wally's
descendants. I believe it is currently in the care of one
of the King's knights called Sir Prysin.

b4284f19-51ab-40cd-a52b-b555cb61a54b.title: Gypsy Aris
b4284f19-51ab-40cd-a52b-b555cb61a54b.text:
He shouldn't be too hard to find. He lives in the royal
palace in this city. Tell him Gypsy Aris sent you.

33c49306-7c76-45a4-b3d8-8a502f9150e0.title: Gypsy Aris
33c49306-7c76-45a4-b3d8-8a502f9150e0.text:
Well if you need any advice I'm always here, young
one.

8081d22b-4816-42c7-b46d-d77cc45ac5f7.title: Gypsy Aris
8081d22b-4816-42c7-b46d-d77cc45ac5f7.text: In the scheme of things you are very young.

options.text: Ok but how old are you?
Oh if it's in the scheme of things that's ok.

26208148-5d77-404b-a45a-d35b4c480b1c.title: <player>
26208148-5d77-404b-a45a-d35b4c480b1c.text: Ok, but how old are you?

46b44f41-ff4e-43cf-b3df-5771bf2de76e.title: Gypsy Aris
46b44f41-ff4e-43cf-b3df-5771bf2de76e.text:
Count the number of legs on the stools in the Blue
Moon inn, and multiply that number by seven.

20ca3adf-a0a8-428d-be74-ea0668c92a65.title: <player>
20ca3adf-a0a8-428d-be74-ea0668c92a65.text: Oh if it's in the scheme of things that's ok.

45b6a2a6-4145-45ff-a3d2-3cc0b1c64d89.title: Gypsy Aris
45b6a2a6-4145-45ff-a3d2-3cc0b1c64d89.text: You show wisdom for one so young.

93538e24-406d-4fc0-8701-169cb424cdf9.title: <player>
93538e24-406d-4fc0-8701-169cb424cdf9.text: Well I'd better press on with it.

3e3b4626-30ea-4b7a-90df-dad21d9dca3a.title: <player>
3e3b4626-30ea-4b7a-90df-dad21d9dca3a.text:
I found Sir Prysin. Unfortunately I haven't got the
sword yet. He's made it complicated for me.

6383e734-ebbc-4a8a-8782-4acd4829f077.title: Gypsy Aris
6383e734-ebbc-4a8a-8782-4acd4829f077.text: Ok, hurry, we haven't much time.

options.text: What is the magical incantation?
Well I'd better press on with it.

064a84ee-b1ed-4faa-8e08-5619b608fc6d.title: <player>
064a84ee-b1ed-4faa-8e08-5619b608fc6d.text: Well I'd better press on with it.

cfe81266-74f6-4eb0-8f01-2d55a6ac5c73.title: <player>
cfe81266-74f6-4eb0-8f01-2d55a6ac5c73.text:
I have the sword now. I just need to kill the demon, I
think.

options.text: What is the magical incantation?
Well I'd better press on with it.
Where can I find the demon?

15a4872e-3070-4646-8f2a-f8379de4a3eb.title: <player>
15a4872e-3070-4646-8f2a-f8379de4a3eb.text: Well I'd better press on with it.

50c95a87-9b83-451f-9c79-d689ec26030b.title: <player>
50c95a87-9b83-451f-9c79-d689ec26030b.text: Where can I find the demon?

6022ac52-d831-4446-bcb3-9ff2abb97939.title: Gypsy Aris
6022ac52-d831-4446-bcb3-9ff2abb97939.text:
Just head south and you should find the stone circle
just outside the city gate.

7ee92cbc-18c7-4428-a795-11311ebc603e.title: Gypsy Aris
7ee92cbc-18c7-4428-a795-11311ebc603e.text:
You're a hero now. That was a good bit of
demonslaying.

options.text: How do you know I killed it?
Thanks.
Stop calling me that!

51bd2f88-c3dc-4ffc-b6f8-39ae3f6c6101.title: <player>
51bd2f88-c3dc-4ffc-b6f8-39ae3f6c6101.text: How do you know I killed it?

71d521cf-6a7f-473a-aea5-37a03d2984b4.title: Gypsy Aris
71d521cf-6a7f-473a-aea5-37a03d2984b4.text: You forget. I'm good at knowing things.

374b5076-30e2-4dd6-ae96-f62f08411e21.title: Gypsy Aris
374b5076-30e2-4dd6-ae96-f62f08411e21.text: In the scheme of things you are very young.

options.text: Ok but how old are you?
Oh if it's in the scheme of things that's ok.

8ddb562b-8a19-480b-b12b-888ad3cf9cc5.title: <player>
8ddb562b-8a19-480b-b12b-888ad3cf9cc5.text: Ok, but how old are you?

4c89e67e-950b-4d57-884f-92dc647dc966.title: Gypsy Aris
4c89e67e-950b-4d57-884f-92dc647dc966.text:
Count the number of legs on the stools in the Blue
Moon inn, and multiply that number by seven.

de28cfce-4e81-4363-92bc-c3a7088d5d56.title: <player>
de28cfce-4e81-4363-92bc-c3a7088d5d56.text: Oh if it's in the scheme of things that's ok.

5060c59b-ac66-4eb6-8af0-4f89268f4218.title: Gypsy Aris
5060c59b-ac66-4eb6-8af0-4f89268f4218.text: You show wisdom for one so young.
